ttp%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FRvOCCMZ.jpg&h=dcbb0cd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/fgcOizF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FfgcOizF.jpg&h=294aa6f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/tltAovI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FtltAovI.jpg&h=51a35f11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/q7Rs8IX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fq7Rs8IX.jpg&h=a61896ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/xpcisD7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FxpcisD7.jpg&h=95bbb16c&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"acc6fc28802fe10a4cd8123d386e491e2cdb3c45","tid":649902,"uid":56649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T01:35:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">班拿貝朝聖指南</div></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>機票</strong><br />\n因航會有直航機，飛大概15個鐘，我好似未見過fanfares有做過馬德里既優惠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (復活節買因航機票六千幾直飛馬德里)<br />\n中東三寶，計埋轉機至少都要19個鐘，我上次搭emirates來回大概$4xxx，飛大概20個鐘<br />\n<br />\n<strong>波飛</strong><br />\n經官網買飛最平，比賽前一個定二個星期開始賣飛，不過有分優先次序，club member &gt; madridista &gt; public<br />\n班拿貝球場出面亦都有個官方櫃台可以俾你買飛，都係比賽前一個定二個星期開始賣飛，每日都會有飛分批出售<br />\n另外官方櫃台出面都有堆人坐係度會係咁問你係咪買飛<br />\n如果係官網買唔到，可以去viagogo, stubhub度買，佢地多數可以一早買定黎緊嗰季既飛，不過通常都係炒價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （我上次係用viagogo買，睇主場對西維爾，坐係同球員通道隔一個block最前排大概$3xxx，y絲睇馬德里打吡，坐兩邊上方，近3000元。）<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: red;\">*注意：賽事有可能會改期，提前好多買飛既巴打自己留意</span></em><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Tour Bernab&eacute;u</strong><br />\n可以參觀班拿貝球場、皇家馬德里博物館、球員休息室、領隊座位與球員後備席<br />\n門票: &euro;25 (手持Madridista: &euro;17)<br />\n開放時間：10:00-19:30 (星期一及星期六)、10:30-18:30 (星期日及假期)<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: red;\">*注意：比賽日開放時間會提早結束，有d地方唔會開放，巴打自己留意</span></em><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Madridista</strong><br />\n即場做madridista有優惠，平過上網申請<br />\n另外球場入面間Adidas madridista有95折，ultra boost嗰啲鞋都照樣有折<br />\n<br />\n<strong>交通</strong><br />\n去班拿貝球場好方便，metro直頭有個班拿貝站，班拿貝站係深藍色10號線，車站兩個出口都係一抬頭就見到球場<br />\n開波前一個鐘左右就入得場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">以上資訊由duckyea!、潺仔、Y_nada_mas、🔥卻老提供</span></span>"},{"pid":"b0c119ebf836780c9703811492470a96071e5ab7","tid":649902,"uid":56649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T01:35:37.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">開post temp</div><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1gWvwGyXQ1NiRgkwk46pIxm8Vvfhwx--29TZYFDGCusI/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1gWvwGyXQ1NiRgkwk46pIxm8Vvfhwx--29TZYFDGCusI%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=U%2FmuvXwI1vujrWW5Gmd3hEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=9681b562\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1gWvwGyXQ1NiRgkwk46pIxm8Vvfhwx--29TZYFDGCusI/edit?usp=sharing</a>"},{"pid":"937bbd26e7e0292a1c333e8b90162a0a5a278b85","tid":649902,"uid":13543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T01:44:01.000Z","msg":"唔小心1001左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62d133d81b1538cba118543ee3b515456e8fd06d","tid":649902,"uid":7123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T01:44:36.000Z","msg":"siu4 一係冇人開 一開開兩個"},{"pid":"8ab47ffbf96256a2398c70e8cf63fb1c6fcdb80b","tid":649902,"uid":171177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T01:45:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"11a7810aad0f832f205826e05981fea4caa91636","tid":649902,"uid":166126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T01:46:23.000Z","msg":"mon左一陣拜post<br />\n今年咁樣走甩球12碼都冇乜屌過我地<br />\n反而上年互有得益就怨成年<br />\n望唔透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgm